data.description: This property boasts 3 bedrooms, 4 full baths, an office/study complete with a desk and built- ins, and an impressive 3,204 sq ft under air. The covered patio area and brick pavers around the pool make for perfect outdoor entertaining. Enjoy the view of the golf course while relaxing in your pool with waterfall feature. Retractable awnings provide shade when you need it. The primary bedroom is outfitted with a large walk-in closet, a cabana bath, and a spacious bath with 2 separate sink areas, a tub,bidet and shower. Your guests will be impressed with the atrium in the guest bedroom, and the wet bar will make entertaining a breeze. The kitchen features granite countertops, lots of storage and an eat-in area. Finally, the office has the space that will make working from home a breeze. Wycliffe Golf & Country Club is a private equity membership club. Recently renovated without a detail missed,this is a top-notch community featuring two championship golf courses, 15 tennis courts and four pickleball courts. A state-of-the-art fitness center,full-service spa and resort-style pool lend to the luxurious lifestyle. With several dining venues and an exhilarating social calendar, there is no shortage of entertainment and enjoyment. Call to schedule a showing today!
